						<summary>

						<p>Basement in front of Nandi <hi rend="italic">maṇḍapa</hi> of Indranāthēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Vijayanagara: Vīra Dēvarāya Mahārāya.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1314 Āṅgīrasa, Vaiśākha śu. 5, Sunday</hi> corresponding to 1392 A.D., May 12.</p>						

						<p>Damaged and built in. It seems to record some gifts of land made probably by the king.</p>						

						</summary>
